40:00.781 --> 40:04.784
You've been lying to me
since the day Mike Ross arrived.

40:07.120 --> 40:10.489
I knew Harvey and Jessica
never really accepted me,

40:10.541 --> 40:12.825
but I thought
you were different.

40:12.876 --> 40:14.827
I thought you were my friend.

40:14.878 --> 40:19.782
- I am your friend, Louis.
- No, you're not.

40:19.800 --> 40:25.171
And don't you ever
say that to me again.

40:25.222 --> 40:27.757
Where are you going?

40:27.791 --> 40:31.928
To see your friend Jessica.

40:37.818 --> 40:40.820
Louis knows.

40:47.194 --> 40:48.778
Louis.

40:48.812 --> 40:50.332
I know you're a stickler
for the rules,

40:50.364 --> 40:52.815
so I figured I'd just
come by to return my I.D.

40:52.833 --> 40:54.149
You want an explanation.

40:54.167 --> 40:55.785
I want to see you
perp walked through the bullpen

40:55.819 --> 40:59.538
with your pretty little jacket
draped over your handcuffs.

40:59.590 --> 41:03.259
But until then, yeah,
I'll take an explanation.

41:03.293 --> 41:07.263
When I found out the truth
about Mike Ross,

41:07.297 --> 41:09.599
it had already been done.

41:09.633 --> 41:12.218
By Harvey?

41:12.269 --> 41:15.688
Right after he
made senior partner over me?

41:15.722 --> 41:17.940
That's when he hired the fraud?

41:17.975 --> 41:19.442
That's the correct timeline,
right?

41:19.476 --> 41:21.027
Yes.

41:21.061 --> 41:22.445
So instead of turning him in,

41:22.479 --> 41:24.614
you cover it up.
Louis-

41:24.648 --> 41:26.983
and the one time
that I do something...

41:27.017 --> 41:30.953
you don't cover it up at all.

41:30.988 --> 41:32.622
You throw me to the wolves.

41:32.656 --> 41:34.740
I saved you from the wolves.

41:34.791 --> 41:37.543
Then I ask you
for the smallest gesture,

41:37.577 --> 41:39.829
just to allow my career
to continue with dignity,

41:39.863 --> 41:44.667
and you couldn't muster
the tiniest shred of compassion.

41:46.803 --> 41:48.421
What do you want me to say?

41:48.472 --> 41:52.875
I want you to tell me
you're a liar!

41:52.893 --> 41:56.896
And a hypocrite!

42:00.600 --> 42:04.603
I want you to say you're sorry.

42:08.158 --> 42:13.946
I am a liar.

42:13.997 --> 42:18.000
And I am a hypocrite.

42:20.236 --> 42:23.456
But I will not say I'm sorry,

42:23.507 --> 42:27.743
because I did what I did
to protect this firm.

42:27.761 --> 42:30.262
Well, looks like the captain's
about to go down with her ship.

42:30.297 --> 42:32.465
Bullshit.

42:32.516 --> 42:34.016
You want something.

42:34.051 --> 42:35.634
Oh, I told you.
I want to see you in...

42:35.686 --> 42:37.553
In handcuffs?

42:37.587 --> 42:41.607
If that were true, the police
would be here instead of you.

42:41.641 --> 42:46.595
No, you wanted to see me squirm

42:46.613 --> 42:50.616
before asking me
for what you really want.

42:53.403 --> 42:56.455
I'm not gonna
give you the satisfaction,

42:56.490 --> 43:00.543
so you might as well
spit it out.

43:00.577 --> 43:02.878
You asked me what I wanted
once before, and I told you,

43:02.913 --> 43:07.616
and then you told me
that I couldn't have it.

43:07.634 --> 43:11.971
But now I can.

43:12.005 --> 43:14.840
Pearson...

43:14.891 --> 43:19.395
Specter...

43:19.429 --> 43:21.347
Litt.

